data.description: What is not to love about this 5BR /2.5 bath home! Large separate dining room off kitchen.   Includes an office and a bonus room off garage with endless options! All bathrooms have been beautifully updated, fresh paint throughout, brand new storm door and ceiling fans. Wait, there is more.  A second  kitchen on the upper floor with a family room and fireplace. Fully fenced backyard and patio for entertaining. For the race lovers, it is a very short walk to the track!
